  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. The sum of the measures of the three interior angles of a triangle is 180&deg;. Therefore, <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"31 plus 2 b, plus a, equals 180\"></span>. Since it&rsquo;s given that <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, equals 45\"></span>, it follows that <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"31 plus 2 b, plus 45, equals 180\"></span>, or <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 b equals 104\"></span>. Dividing both sides of this equation by 2 yields <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"b equals 52\"></span>.<p>Choice B is incorrect and may result from a calculation error. Choice C is incorrect. This is the value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"a, plus 31 \"></span>. Choice D is incorrect. This is the value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"2 b\"></span>.</p></p>\n",
